{"tid":631902,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"痴線！德甲球證睇完VAR   半場休息叫球員出返嚟射12碼","createTime":"2018-04-17T02:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T00:52:25.000Z","uid":4661,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"c645b7f2efea401c5272f22076e7422afb25caa4","tid":631902,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zL0k9qLindk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzL0k9qLindk&d=HpNC7wmU2S%2F5YZmBUwkU60bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0909c064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zL0k9qLindk</a><br />\n<br />\n德甲周一晚緬恩斯主場對弗賴堡的護級大戰，出現了可能稱得上為視像裁判系統（VAR）啟用以來的最大鬧劇。球證雲克文（Guido Winkmann）在上半場鳴笛後，雙方球員已經離開球場步入更衣室後，忽然透過VAR重看比賽畫面，然後判弗賴堡的球員犯手球。<br />\n<br />\n球證作出判決後，要求兩隊球員重返球場，讓緬恩斯的球員主射12碼。極刑由主隊中場柏保路巴拉斯操刀得手，當上半場真正完結時，緬恩斯領先1:0。其實在上半場仍在進行時，緬恩斯右閘保辛斯基傳中後，皮球疑似省中客隊中堅甘普夫的手，皮球飛向球門，最終被弗賴堡門將舒禾路撲出。當時主隊球員已經提出要得到12碼，但球證雲克文未有理會。當兩隊球員步離球場時，球證雲克文受到指示下以VAR重看比賽畫面，然後推翻自己之前的決定，判緬恩斯得到一記12碼。<br />\n<br />\n下半場比賽因為有大批球迷將一卷又一卷的廁紙從看台後方摘出，因而要押後開始。英國《BBC》報道指，球迷的舉動與上半場的12碼並無關係，純粹是因為球迷不滿比賽安排在周一晚上進行。緬恩斯中場柏保路巴拉斯在完場前11分鐘把握弗賴堡門將犯錯再入一球，最終助球隊在這場護級大戰中勝出。<br />\n<br />\n緬恩斯全取三分後，暫時以較佳得失球差壓過同樣30戰得30分的弗賴堡，脫離降班漩渦，但德甲排名14至16位的三支球隊，其實都只得30分在手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180417/large/1523915346_1901.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F1523915346_1901.jpg&h=9b1caed0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f7c58c3629cd88d1c0ea6ec42987f5bb1c8371b","tid":631902,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:04:27.000Z","msg":"試下完場再吹"},{"pid":"4648a64b539a351b426b929eee05cc1f6a74b338","tid":631902,"uid":31314,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:04:40.000Z","msg":"點解會有咁多廁紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e0d7024214ebf5bdd10cd73b13582ae9b38f50","tid":631902,"uid":34490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180417/large/1523915346_1901.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F1523915346_1901.jpg&h=9b1caed0&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b491c11b6ace2fc883b6ad1a361f7bca3b11de4c","tid":631902,"uid":50385,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:06:00.000Z","msg":"球證醒唔起自己買咗半主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fd53130b214985758385a6dac13aad718130be","tid":631902,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:06:14.000Z","msg":"掟廁紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025725efba599633a89e9a9d9f727b1f6930114c","tid":631902,"uid":179672,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:06:25.000Z","msg":"又幾靚"},{"pid":"29243042152874aa28ef9ce7e628af7bd1f7ad3e","tid":631902,"uid":1441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9fd53130b214985758385a6dac13aad718130be","tid":631902,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:06:14.000Z","msg":"掟廁紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:07:27.000Z","msg":"以前香港大球場都經常有人咁做"},{"pid":"2f8d24ba9d893d71f6db46399d3405ac781a7f05","tid":631902,"uid":62971,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:07:44.000Z","msg":"如果英超有VAR ，咁完場係咪要叫牙傾出黎入波？"},{"pid":"f2d84bf5633bcca1d2cc73ea5a0595a1db0333aa","tid":631902,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike"